Crypto Price Tracker
====================

Files:
- main.py            : Command-line tracker (polling, CSV logging, threshold alerts, portfolio)
- streamlit_app.py   :  Streamlit dashboard
- requirements.txt

Quick start:
1) Create a virtualenv and install:
   python -m venv venv
   source venv/bin/activate  # or venv\\Scripts\\activate on Windows
   pip install -r requirements.txt

2) Run CLI:
   python main.py --symbols BTC ETH --interval 15 --csv prices.csv
   Example with threshold and holdings:
   python main.py -s BTC ETH ADA -i 10 -c prices.csv -t BTC:60000 -t ETH:3000 -H BTC:0.1 -H ETH:1.2

3) Run once:
   python main.py --symbols BTC ETH --run-once

4) Generate plots after stop:
   python main.py --symbols BTC ETH -c prices.csv --plot

5) Optional GUI:
   streamlit run streamlit_app.py

Telegram alerts (optional):
- Create a bot and get token, and your chat id.
- Run with --telegram-token <TOKEN> --telegram-chat-id <CHAT_ID>

Notes:
- Uses CoinGecko simple price API (no API key).


